milestones.description: Holder has conceded the most runs in an innings (56) in ODIs for WI, going past Keith Boyce's record of 47
Asif Masood has conceded the most runs in an innings (64) in ODIs for PAK, going past Sarfraz Nawaz's record of 63
Keith Boyce has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for WI, going past Fredericks
Asif Masood has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (5) for PAK, going past Asif Iqbal
Deryck Murray and Andy Roberts's 64-run partnership is the highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 28 between de Silva and Kaluperuma
Rohan Kanhai and Clive Lloyd's 48-run partnership is WI's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 17 between Clive Lloyd and Alvin Kallicharran
Clive Lloyd and Viv Richards's 15-run partnership is WI's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Garry Sobers and Alvin Kallicharran
Deryck Murray and Keith Boyce's 15-run partnership is WI's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Deryck Murray and Keith Boyce
Deryck Murray and Holder's 37-run partnership is WI's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 22 between Deryck Murray and Holder
Mushtaq Mohammad and Majid Khan's 57-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 41 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Majid Khan
Mushtaq Mohammad and Wasim Raja's 62-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 47 between Mushtaq Mohammad and Asif Iqbal
Pervez Mir and Javed Miandad's 14-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Imran Khan and Wasim Raja
